{"tid":520242,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦又壞L左...懇請各大神指教","createTime":"2018-01-05T08:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T07:06:11.000Z","uid":101246,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6f341d1571b6fe85acb8309f821f085739f311b0","tid":520242,"uid":101246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:22:24.000Z","msg":"件事就係咁既，前日部腦仲好地地打緊LOL,<br />\n琴日就開左機大概一分鐘左右就自己熄左機..咩反應都冇，求電腦大神指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下都係開左機啲畫面，有時未倒數完都熄L左機，加上唔知點解我依個畫面我係用唔到keyboard...只好等佢倒數。另外都有試過用碟開機，但結果都係一樣load緊隻碟就自己熄機..<br />\n<br />\n之後我自己打開左個主機，發現風扇同粒cpu因為冇哂散熱膏導致解左體，唔知又係咪咁既原因導致開唔到機？<br />\n<br />\n求大神指點小弟迷津<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/161608_d7c706d2c9b940dc0d7d01cc3b795885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F161608_d7c706d2c9b940dc0d7d01cc3b795885.jpg&h=154cfab1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/161632_9cb81d5180bcb8326360c78e55dd6bd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F161632_9cb81d5180bcb8326360c78e55dd6bd7.jpg&h=45b08be7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/161650_15a8612985307b378c2bfc287778619d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F161650_15a8612985307b378c2bfc287778619d.jpg&h=8d733628&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a865e0099a3ce092abb2c892682594df742747f","tid":520242,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:28:15.000Z","msg":"今年讀幾年級？"},{"pid":"f7c76d41b159d649fcddf05356d41775165fba05","tid":520242,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:33:29.000Z","msg":"cpu 出煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" cla